Anke Pietrangeli (amụrụ n'abalị́ iri na isii nke ọnwa Nọvemba afọ 1982) bụ onye South Africa na-agụ egwu
Ọ bụ onye mmeri nke oge nke abụọ nke usoro ọchụchọ talent a ma ama  bụ Idols na South Africa n'afọ 2003. Dị ka onye bu ya ụzọ, Heinz Winckler, Anke nwekwara aha njirimara: The Kimberley Diamond
Nwanne ya nwoke, Sven, kwenyesiri Pietrangeli ike ịbanye, onye ji n'aka mgbe niile na nwanne ya nwanyị ga-abụ onye ama ama.
